        <screen><computeroutput>usage: glance member-create [--can-share] &lt;IMAGE&gt; &lt;TENANT_ID&gt;
        </computeroutput></screen>
        <para>
Share a specific image with a tenant.
        </para>  <variablelist wordsize="10">
